name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: ( t1.`IS_ARCHIVED` = 0  AND  t1.`IS_DELETED` = 0  AND  (select count(1) from favorite where create_man=#{ctx.sessioncontext.srfpersonid} and OWNER_ID=t1.`ID` ) = '1' )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.expression: (select count(1) from favorite where create_man=#{ctx.sessioncontext.srfpersonid} and OWNER_ID=t1.`ID` )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeExps.name: IS_FAVORITE

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`COLOR`,
t1.`CREATE_MAN`,
t1.`CREATE_TIME`,
t1.`DESCRIPTION`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`IDENTIFIER`,
t1.`IS_ARCHIVED`,
t1.`IS_DELETED`,
(select count(1) from favorite where create_man=#{ctx.sessioncontext.srfpersonid} and OWNER_ID=t1.`ID` ) AS `IS_FAVORITE`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`UPDATE_MAN`,
t1.`UPDATE_TIME`,
t1.`VISIBILITY`
FROM `LIBRARY` t1
